showdown.abilities.mindseye.name=Mind's Eye
showdown.abilities.mindseye.desc=This Pokémon can hit Ghost types with Normal- and Fighting-type moves. Prevents other Pokémon from lowering this Pokémon's accuracy stat stage. This Pokémon ignores a target's evasiveness stat stage.
