showdown.moves.roleplay.name=Role Play
showdown.moves.roleplay.desc=A Habilidade do usuário muda para corresponder à Habilidade do alvo. Falha se a habilidade do usuário for As One, Battle Bond, Comatose, Commander, Disguise, Gulp Missile, Hadron Engine, Ice Face, Multitype, Orichalcum Pulse, Power Construct, Protosynthesis, Quark Drive, RKS System, Schooling, Shields Down, Stance Change , Modo Zen, Zero para Herói, ou já corresponde ao alvo, ou se a habilidade do alvo for As One, Battle Bond, Comatose, Commander, Disguise, Flower Gift, Forecast, Gulp Missile, Hadron Engine, Hunger Switch, Ice Face, Illusion , Imposter, Multitype, Neutralizing Gas, Orichalcum Pulse, Power Construct, Power of Alchemy, Protosynthesis, Quark Drive, Receiver, RKS System, Schooling, Shields Down, Stance Change, Trace, Wonder Guard, Zen Mode ou Zero to Hero.
